dct_description_sm: This line dataset shapefile the state, federal, and interstate highways that are located within the extent of the Russian River basin.

The intended purpose of this layer is to provide users with information describing state, federal, and interstate highways with the Russian River basin. This layer allows users access to major road information in this region without having to select these features from larger roads datasets.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
